This creamy tuna pasta bake is the perfect recipe to recreate if you are looking for a wholesome but quick and easy meal to end off your week.  If you are looking for a vegetarian option then you can leave out the tuna and still enjoy the yummy, creamy, and cheesy pasta bake your family will be sure to love.  Serve your delicious and creamy tuna pasta bake dish with your favourite fresh side salad for supper tonight. ALSO TRY: Recipe of the day: 30-minute roasted pork tenderloin This recipe was found on kitchensanctuary.com